IV. SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
JAVA 1.6 or higher.
JDK 1.6 or higher is required for building
Current make script is for windows only

V. USING THE LIBRARY
Import the jar file into eclipse or add the jar file to 
the class path

VI. RUNNING THE SAMPLES
From eclipse, navigate to the sample and press run.
Make sure the library file is in the referenced libraries

From the command line, add the jar file to the class path
and either navigate to the directory and run it or

java -cp "jars/*" package_name.class_name